subjectList.answer:
参考程序：

n=int(input())
a=[]
for i in range(n + 1):
     a.append(-1)
for i in range(1,n + 1):
   for j in range(1,n + 1):
      if(j % i ) == 0:
        a[j] =  a[j] * -1
s=0
for i in range(1,n + 1):
   if (a[i] == 1):

print(s)
